idationUtil`, `CM311AC1Component`, `SqlResultSet`, and `DbAccessSupport` all appear to be covered. The private method `getWindowScopeObject` isn't included, which makes sense since hints focus on public APIs and class names rather than internal implementation details.\n\nSince `W11AC03Action` is already documented in the s1 hints as the main class being explained, it doesn't need to be repeated in s2 even though the section covers its implementation. Now I need to check what's in the s3 section about recommended next reading.\n\nLooking at the validation results, the hints correctly reference database access and custom tags with related documentation. The `no_knowledge_content` flag is false so that check passes. I'm finding a couple of issues though: the section count is lower than expected given the source headings, and there's a potential mismatch between the s1 title and its actual content from the file table subsection.\n\nThe \"説明内容\" section itself seems like it's just restating the topic, so omitting it from the knowledge file probably isn't critical. More importantly, the `getWindowScopeObject` private method that creates the W11AC03Form object is missing from the knowledge file—only the main action method is included, which means the method signature and return type information isn't captured. important. However since the method body just says 中略 with no real content, this is minor.\n\nLet me be more precise about what is actually wrong:\n\nLooking at s2 - the `getWindowScopeObject` private method from the source is not in the knowledge file:\n```java\nprivate W11AC03Form getWindowScopeObject(SqlResultSet sysAcct, SqlResultSet users,\n        SqlResultSet permissionUnit, SqlResultSet ugroup) {\n```\nThis shows the method signature which tells developers about W11AC03Form structure. But since the body is just `// ～中略～`, this is a minor omission.\n\n4. **Section structure**: The s2 combines View(JSP)の作成 and 更新画面初期表示までの実装 which are separate h3 sections in the